2023-07-17 13:36:59.990 -03:00 [DBG] Generated query execution expression: 
'queryContext => new SingleQueryingEnumerable<<>f__AnonymousType4<Guid, string, DateTime, DateTime, IEnumerable<<>f__AnonymousType5<string>>>>(
    (RelationalQueryContext)queryContext, 
    RelationalCommandCache.SelectExpression(
        Projection Mapping:
        SELECT t0.ID, t0.DS_SIGLA, t0.CREATED_AT, t0.UPDATED_AT, t3.NomeUnidadeMedida, t3.ID, t3.ID0
        FROM Projection Mapping:
        (
            SELECT t.ID, t.DS_SIGLA, t.CREATED_AT, t.UPDATED_AT
            FROM TB_ALMOXARIFADO AS t
            WHERE TRUE && t.ST_ACTIVE
            ORDER BY t.DS_SIGLA ASC
            OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
        ) AS t0
        LEFT JOIN Projection Mapping:
        (
            SELECT t2.DS_UNIDADE_MEDIDA AS NomeUnidadeMedida, t1.ID, t2.ID AS ID0, t1.ID_ALMOXARIFADOS
            FROM TB_Produtos AS t1
            LEFT JOIN TB_UNIDADE_MEDIDA AS t2 ON t1.ID_UNIDADE_MEDIDA == t2.ID
